#81  Dirk Morgna returns--but will this "Sun Boy" join the Legion or engulf it in an all-consuming inferno? 

#82  The Legion's mission to Starboy's home planet turns downright weird when the team is attacked by a group of rogue heroes. Plus, Ultra Boy discovers the shocking cause of his recent bouts of pain. 

#83  The Emerald Empress becomes the team's greatest threat yet as one Legionnaire pays a terrible price in a futile attempt to save a friend. 

#84  The entire Legion succumbs to the Emerald Eye's power, kicking off an all-new direction for the heroes of the future.
